{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_08_01",
  "title": "早坂芽衣",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣とすずが……あの二人がこんな素晴らしい\nパフォーマンスをする日が来るとはなぁ……",
      "startTime": 5.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3433.3333334000013,
          "startTime": 8.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、来たよー！\nあれ？　何観てるの？",
      "startTime": 13.2999994279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "この間あった\nユニットバトルの大会の動画を観てたんだよ",
      "startTime": 16.9333327612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "動画サイトで全試合が配信されてるんだよね\n芽衣もちょこっと観たよ",
      "startTime": 23.8666660946,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お、コメント欄で\n芽衣とすずが絶賛されているぞ",
      "startTime": 27.5000004452,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "わっ……ほんとだ\nえへへ、照れちゃうな～",
      "startTime": 33.7666671118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "でも……うん、やっぱり嬉しいな\nこうやってみんなに認めてもらえるのって",
      "startTime": 43.1666671118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "曲を作るまではいろいろあって大変だったけど……\nみんなの前で歌った時は本当に楽しかったんだ",
      "startTime": 50.8333368303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、すずにゃんとユニットを組めて\nほんとに良かった",
      "startTime": 59.7000017168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、終わっちゃうと\nちょっとだけ寂しいな～",
      "startTime": 65.1333386105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "今日はちょうどその話をしようと思ってたんだ\n芽衣とすずの曲をリリースすることになったぞ",
      "startTime": 71.5333386105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……うん、そうだよね\n芽衣とすずにゃんの曲をリリース……",
      "startTime": 80.8666719438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "……え、リリース？\nえぇぇぇ～～！？　ほんと！？　ほんとに！？",
      "startTime": 86.8000052771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "期間限定のはずだったんだが、ステージの評判が\n相当良くてな……って、こらこら、近い近い！",
      "startTime": 93.5333386105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇねぇ、リリースするってことは\nレコーディングとかジャケット撮影もあるんだよね！？",
      "startTime": 100.7666714352,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "やったー！　早くすずにゃんに教えなきゃ！",
      "startTime": 104.3333340329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すずならさっき仕事が終わったから\nもうじき戻って……",
      "startTime": 111.9666683835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "むむ！　あそこにいるのは～……すずにゃんだね！\nすずにゃ～ん！　大変たいへ～～ん！",
      "startTime": 119.3666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8466.666666600006,
          "startTime": 127.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "すっごい嬉しいニュースだよー！\n落ち着いて聞いてね～～！",
      "startTime": 126.2999859495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が落ち着いた方が……って、行ってしまった\nよっぽど嬉しいんだな",
      "startTime": 134.2333447141,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣とすずは……今回の一件で\nさらに絆が深まったみたいだな",
      "startTime": 139.7666780474,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 143.3333447141,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1199.988619199985,
          "startTime": 144.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4433.321952599982,
          "startTime": 147.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.4333457313
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.4333457313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すずにゃんからだ！\nえ～と、なになに……",
      "startTime": 149.3000215533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.66668822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～！？\nそんな～……どうしよ～",
      "startTime": 154.16668822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.66668822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何かあったのか？",
      "startTime": 158.66668822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "今日はね、この後すずにゃんと出掛ける予定だったんだ",
      "startTime": 161.3333548866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.36668822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "さっき撮影が終わったばかりなのに、芽衣は元気だな",
      "startTime": 166.36668822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、すずにゃんが仕事なのを忘れてたみたいで\n来れなくなっちゃってさ～",
      "startTime": 175.26668822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.2333436968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "ユニットバトルの大会本番までは\nずーっと練習漬けだったし",
      "startTime": 180.7333436968,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "大会が終わった後もなかなか予定が合わなくて……\n今日は久しぶりに二人で出掛けられると思ったのにな～",
      "startTime": 188.2666658404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.6999991737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……それは残念だな\nちなみに、何をする予定だったんだ？",
      "startTime": 195.8999991737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "えっとね、まずは寮の買い出しをして\n後はい～っぱい遊ぶつもりだったよ",
      "startTime": 201.900000191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 205.7333386106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei021.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　{user}さん\nなんでそんなこと聞いたの？",
      "startTime": 208.2666719439,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 210.7333386106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_08_01-mei022.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして～……\nすずにゃんのかわりに遊んでくれるとか！？",
